            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>basil </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop the <strong>reserved tomato flesh</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>sultanas</strong> to a small bowl and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong>, then set aside to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
