    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roughly chop the <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong></p><p>Mix the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>sun-dried tomatoes </strong>with the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>soft cheese </strong>– this is your <strong>sun-dried tomato mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
